{"tid":302152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【習總訪港】午膳時間封橋罰企 OL：呢餐飯要食快啲","createTime":"2017-06-29T07:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T11:06:59.000Z","uid":122,"like":9,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2105857e9e9ac1589af684d7f2b2b68fbc08fdac","tid":302152,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170629/large/1498715077_82a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170629%2Flarge%2F1498715077_82a3.jpg&h=3b0341e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因封橋等候的OL表示「呢餐飯要食快啲、急啲。」（麥超億攝）<br />\n<br />\n因應國家主席習近平入住萬麗海景酒店，警方昨下午１時許突然封閉由會展廣場通往鷹君中心及中環廣場的天橋，過百名原準備往吃午飯的白領上班族要在天橋口「罰企」，被問到「封橋罰企」阻礙午飯時間，有不願透露姓名的OL大嘆無奈：「咁冇辦法！」她說只得1小時的午飯時間，「佢（警方）冇講明封幾耐，問佢就話封10分鐘！」該女士稱：「呢餐飯要食快啲、急啲。」結果封橋封了12分鐘便重開，上班族馬上急步而行，趕往「醫肚」。"},{"pid":"916bb89133949f4ad0fdf09be76612e3a6f7b283","tid":302152,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:30:15.000Z","msg":"又話ol，圖文不符喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9e1f393a400df0ffd7b48f4ef4dfbe875ac711","tid":302152,"uid":29539,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"OL = old lady?"},{"pid":"f61e4c34111728fcafc326faef039bd24ab8a729","tid":302152,"uid":121409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話ol，圖文不符喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nold lady<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b131968ab3d0d90bd080af7cff363369aa5c750","tid":302152,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:31:24.000Z","msg":"OL？你識唔識英文呀屌你老母？"},{"pid":"ff0b2060f8f24dac25cb69f167bc9df718ee7bf8","tid":302152,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20